query:
SELECT
                id,
                workflow_type,
                workflow_id,
                payload,
                attempts,
                last_error,
                created_at
            FROM ironflow.outbox
            WHERE processed_at IS NULL
              AND attempts >= $1
              AND ($2::text IS NULL OR workflow_type = $2)
              AND ($3::text IS NULL OR workflow_id = $3)
            ORDER BY created_at DESC
            LIMIT $4
